{{primary sources|date=December 2009}} {{Infobox company | name = Baker Tilly Virchow Krause, LLP | image = [[File:Baker Tilly Logo.svg|200px]] | trading_name = Baker Tilly | type = Accountancy firm | industry = [[Professional services]] | foundation = 1931 | location_city = [[Chicago]], [[Illinois]] | locations = | area_served = United States | key_people = Alan D. Whitman {{small|([[Chairman]] & [[CEO]])}}<ref>{{cite web| url=https://bakertilly.com/contact/directory/alan-whitman|title=Directory: Alan D. Whitman|accessdate=28 November 2018|publisher=Baker Tilly}}</ref> | revenue = {{profit}} [[United States dollar|US$]]546 million (2017)<ref name=annualreport2017>{{cite web|title=Baker Tilly Annual Report 2017|url=https://www.bakertilly.com/annualreport2017/|website=bakertilly.com|accessdate=28 November 2018}}</ref> | operating_income = | net_income = | num_employees = 2,700 (2017)<ref name=annualreport2017/> | divisions = | footnotes = | location_country = [[United States]] | homepage = {{url|http://www.bakertilly.com}} }}
'''Baker Tilly Virchow Krause, LLP''' (doing business as '''Baker Tilly''') is a [[public accounting]] and [[consulting firm]] headquartered in Chicago, Illinois. Formerly known as Virchow, Krause & Company, LLP, the firm is the American member of [[Baker Tilly International]], a global [[accounting network]] headquartered in [[London]], [[United Kingdom]]. Having joined Baker Tilly International in 1999,<ref>{{cite web| url= https://www.accountingtoday.com/news/virchow-krause-changes-name-to-baker-tilly|title= Virchow Krause Changes Name to Baker Tilly|accessdate=28 November 2018|publisher=Accounting Today}}</ref> the firm officially adopted the Baker Tilly name on June 01, 2009.<ref>{{cite web| url= http://www.bakertillyinternational.com/web/news/2009/june/virchow-krause-company,-llp-rebrands-as-baker-tilly.aspx|title= Virchow Krause & Company, LLP Rebrands as Baker Tilly|accessdate=28 November 2018|publisher=Baker Tilly International}}</ref> Vault Accounting 50 has ranked Baker Tilly Virchow Krause, LLP as the 9th most prestigious accounting firm in their 2019 ranking.<ref>{{cite web| url= http://www.vault.com/company-rankings/accounting/most-prestigious-accounting-firms/?sRankID=178&pg=5|title= 2019 Most Prestigious Accounting Firms|accessdate=28 November 2018|publisher=Vault}}</ref>
==History== The firm originated in 1931 and the present partnership was organized in 1953.
On June 1, 2009, the former Virchow, Krause & Company, LLP changed its name to Baker Tilly Virchow Krause, LLP, becoming the only U.S. member of the [[Baker Tilly International]] network to be branded as "Baker Tilly".
Baker Tilly Virchow Krause, LLP merged with Philadelphia-based ParenteBeard, LLC effective October 1, 2014.
==Primary services== *Auditing and Accounting *Management Consulting *Tax Consulting and Compliance *Forensic, Litigation, and Valuation Services
==Locations== Baker Tilly currently has 33 offices throughout 13 states in the [[Northeastern United States|Northeast]], [[Midwestern United States|Midwest]] and [[Southern United States|South]].
The Baker Tilly headquarters is located in [[Chicago]] and the firm has another office in [[Illinois]] as well.
There are also offices located in [[Delaware]], [[Georgia (U.S. state)|Georgia]], [[Maryland]], [[Michigan]], [[Minnesota]], [[New Jersey]], [[New York (state)|New York]], [[Oklahoma]], [[Pennsylvania]], [[Texas]], [[Washington Metropolitan Area|Washington DC]], and [[Wisconsin]].<ref>{{cite web|title=BakerTilly.com|url=https://www.bakertilly.com/office-locations}}</ref>
==Ranking== Baker Tilly is the 13th largest [[certified public accountant|CPA]] and consulting firm in the United States.<ref>[https://www.accountingtoday.com/the-2017-top-100-firms-and-regional-leaders 2017 Public Accounting Today's “Top 100 Firms"]</ref>
Baker Tilly has been recognized as a "Best Places to Work" for women. Baker Tilly was awarded "Best Places to Work" in both Chicago and Minneapolis.{{when|date=September 2012}}{{citation needed|date=September 2012}}
[[Baker Tilly International]] is the 8th largest worldwide accounting network.
